OL,3,CMichelle Donelan apologises for making
OL,4,CHamas claim on social media
OL,6,FProfessor Dibyesh Anand was included,
OL,7,Falongside Prof Sang, in a piece by
OL,8,Fthink tank Policy Exchange, which put
OL,9,Fout what lawyers have called a
OL,10,F"seriously misleading press release"
OL,11,Fabout the academics' comments.
OL,13,FThe report was released on the same
OL,14,Fday that Ms Donelan published her
OL,15,Fletter accusing Prof Sang of being a
OL,16,FHamas sympathiser.
OL,18,FProf Anand said the "attack was
OL,19,Fideological" and done without "serious
OL,20,Fquestioning" of his and his
OL,21,Fcolleague's work.
